Friday is his funeral so parents are going to be going and I might go and then get a ride back with my bro Patrick b/c I'm watching his kids while him and his wife go somewhere for dinner or I'll stay home and have another ride or parents be back in time to take me to Pat and Angie's house by 6pm not quite sure. A friend told me today if you really want to be a journalist you gotta be able to write everyday and they are absouletly right..so now on my thing is going to be writting in here everyday and if I don't have time one day then I will write double on the day on the next day. I must first come to realize I'm not alone in this world because hell I'm not.I have great friends. I might not see them alot but at least I know I can always call them and they will either answer then or if I leave a message they will get to me as soon as possible. 

 I've been  doing well in school and its become like my life to get good grades and my parents and I are working on bonding.They want me to be more open and talk to them about anything like I use to do when I was in High School but now I'm becoming more distant because I'm afraid they won't approve or they'll get angry or they will think I'm becoming someone they don't want to know.Sometimes I honestly feel like I'm not good enough for my parents or my family and knowing the fact that I don't even know my real parents and that I'm adopted doesn't make things better. Just the only thing I don't want to go looking for my parents alone . I WANT TO BE WITH SOMEONE..doesn't matter someone I can trust and know will be there for me when I find my real parent ...I've come to realize I dont have any friends who have time for me and yet I don't have time for them that needs to change some how.  I don't honestly know who even likes me anymore and I lost andrew which isnt surprise to me, because it was mostly my fault because of reasons most people if they know me know. I just should you know try to be single for a while, find myself first. Figure out where really is my heart and soul right now and where do I want it to be and even though I didn't want to face it..loosing Andrew I knew it was going to happen one way or another because we weren't talking as much and well stuff happens..relationships end and you gott move and one of my parents best friend is dying and will probaly be gone tomorrow or lastest thursday and i dont know. i just feel lonely for some odd reason..I Don't know exactly how to describe it. But probaly the only way I'll fall asleep to night is just crying myself to sleep. My spring break starts Friday thank god for that...I need the break from school even though I have no plans right now for the whole week I'm off.Maybe If I'm lucky I'll get to spend a day with my best friend in Daytona Beach and maybe my parents and I will bond better. Who knows? well its 10:32pm and I must be off to bed I don't have humanities class until 2:30pm but I have to wake up early b/c might be going to church w/ parents tomorrow morning and cleaning people are coming and have to finish up on my speech on types of dreams that i have to talk about on Wednesday afternoon. I got B on math test I took last Wednesday so I don't have to go class this Wednesday , so I don't have math until spring break is over so I only have 3 classes left this week instead of 4. Well I am off to bed for real this time . good luck and goodnight.
<3 Donna

Hey Holy crap the last time I wrote on hear was 9/22/05. Lots has happen since then...had to reactivate this account b/c it was like unactivated and ready to delete itself and yet I activated it and everything I wrote is still here...I've graduated From Bishoop Moore High School and now Freshmen in second semester @ Valencia Community College majoring in journalism...wow been almost a year since I haven't been anywhere near BMCHS.I'll be 20 in 3 months before you know it...really don't know what to say or talk about...I've meet a few new people @ Vcc..Classes are going well for me I guess you say.I have liked all my teachers so far and have a's & b's . I still write poetry every now and then... when I'm inspired or in the mood.

I'm making new live journal when i get home around 6:30ish unless I get home sooner. Tomorrow I have class at 9am-11:45am and then probaly to the beach mid afternoon and hanging out with Matt Stone on Saturday. I am not sure if i can go to kara's bday party or not I mean I'll be in Winter Park October 7-9 but my parents dont really have time to take me and i doubt I'll have time to get my liscence by then even though i should of gotten it months ago but yeah w/e almost 10 months with andrew I'm happy .Nothing can take him away from me and vice versa I'm writting him a letter for our one year anniversary. :) its all from my heart :)

I feel like i'm loosing everyone I've ever cared about ...all my friends are starting to desert me and  don't think it doesn't bother me and I'm trying to not let it get to me but if you have any idea how it is to to loose a best friend or have your friends or now your so called friends backstab you after years of you trusting them you know exactly how I feel...and this whole coming week just plain sucks right now I thought I was going to at least have a great weekend and now it seems like everything is going to hell...down hill. I was looking forward to spending time with Andrew who I haven't seen for over a week and now it'll be two weeks and it could be up to a month or more at this rate...I got a phone call from him that made my mood go from being at least little bit happy knowing I had him and will see him Friday  to pretty upset because now there is no chance at all I'm seeing him Friday or this Sunday at my youthgroup...because he didn't have his birth certificate to get his permit so he is not allowed to see me for while and his mom said something about cutting us off ....breaking us up...so he called me himself to explain that and yet still said I love you and I'll call you later tonight so I have no idea what exactly is going to happen I really don't know if we are still together as a couple or not anymore and I don't even want to ask him ...I'm afraid of the answer...I don't want to loose Andrew I really love him and three months is long time compared to any relationship I've had in a long time. I promised myself I wouldn't cry over anything ever again or get depressed because things happens for a reason but I'm about to just break my promise and start crying..and I dont even have a damn friend to talk to right now about this I'm sick to my stomache also because I withdrew over a week ago of my medication for my acid reflux and now that I've totally screwed myself over I'm going to have to start again soon like tomorrow ....Gosh darn it  I'm crying now I'm done writting...if anyone cares enough about me to try to cheer me up IM me on Sweetietart522 or drownnmylove4eva

Then after the millenia mall which we were only there for like 10-15 mins we drove to the Florida Mall and walked around and went to Sharper Image and then I went into Hot Topic and bought a Green Day Poster while my dad was in FYE ..I have no idea what he bought and he wouldnt let me know so probaly something for me I'll find out tomorrow! My mom bought for us a DVD/CD/VCR player but we didnt tell my dad until he took out almost the same kind as my mom which he bought from FYE and my mom and I gave each other like "oh no" look it was pretty funny. So now we have two dvd players . So the one my dad got is staying here and the one my mom bought is going to Daytona Beach.  I bought my dad a Ray Charlies Cd and my mom and I got him Senfield Season 1 & 2 dvd series and another dvd of comedy movies and my dad and I got my mom one trivia quiz book thingy from barnes and noble and two art books .I know I got some clothes from my mom but I have no idea what else my mom or my dad got me . I am actually sorta happy tomorrow is christmas even though I'm still sort of sad and sick i am going to make it a good christmas. I am in happy mood b/c I talked to Andrew for 11 mins on the phone tonight 2 hours ago and he's so sweet. He said "you know what I wish I could have for  christmas?" and I was like "what?" and he goes " you...to be with you for christmas and not 4 hours away in Miami" and I was just like "aw omg same here" and then he sort of sighed so cute and then he was like " I  love you" and I was like "same here" gosh I love his voice! He comes Jan 2nd on Sunday..day before School starts but I dont know what time he'll be home. So I don't know if him and I'll get the chance to hang out or not..If my church has youthgroup I'm going to ask him to come if he can! Ok well Merry Christmas everyone!

~D
